# Garnet build + cache artifacts.
#
# The HMAC'd cache (v3.3 CacheHMAC) under .garnet-cache/ is machine-
# specific; never commit it. The target/ and build/ trees follow the
# same pattern as Cargo.
.garnet-cache/
target/
build/

# Signed-manifest keyfiles. Anything ending in .key is treated as
# secret by convention. If you commit a .key by accident, rotate it
# via `garnet keygen <newfile>` and stop trusting the old pubkey.
*.key

# IDE + editor scratch.
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*~

# Platform artifacts.
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
